<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="px-4 py-5">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Welcome to DarkVault</h1>
                    <p class="lead">A deliberately vulnerable web application for security training</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">Practice identifying and exploiting common web vulnerabilities in a safe environment</p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">Login</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">Register</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">Featured Vulnerabilities</h5>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            SQL Injection
                            <span class="badge bg-danger rounded-pill">High Risk</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)
                            <span class="badge bg-danger rounded-pill">High Risk</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            Insecure Direct Object References
                            <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark rounded-pill">Medium Risk</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            Path Traversal
                            <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark rounded-pill">Medium Risk</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            Command Injection
                            <span class="badge bg-danger rounded-pill">High Risk</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> Practice Security Testing</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Safely explore and exploit web vulnerabilities without risking real systems. Perfect for security students and professionals.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-journal-code"></i> Learn by Doing</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Understand how vulnerabilities work by exploiting them directly. Hands-on experience is the best teacher.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-graph-up"></i> Track Your Progress</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Collect flags as you successfully exploit vulnerabilities and monitor your growing security skills.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-warning mt-5" role="alert">
            <h4 class="alert-heading"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i> Warning!</h4>
            <p>This application contains intentional security vulnerabilities. It is designed for educational purposes only.</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="mb-0">Do not deploy in production environments or expose to public networks. Use only in isolated training environments.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white mt-5 py-4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>DarkVault</h5>
                    <p>A deliberately vulnerable web application for security training.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
                    <p><small>For educational purposes only. Created for web application security testing practice.</small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 